iella |url=http://www.lagunabeachindy.com/laguna-beach-mother-writes-for-lifetime-tv/ |title=Laguna Beach Local News Children Grown, Mom Returns to TV |publisher=lagunabeachindy.com |date= December 17, 2014|accessdate=December 17, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Walk. Ride. Rodeo.]]'' \n| 2019\n| Diego\n| {{sort|Allyn|Conor Allyn}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Principal photography began in [[New Mexico]] in July 2018.}}\n|-\n!scope=row| ''Witches in the Woods''\n| 2019\n| Philip\n| {{sort|Barker|Jordan Barker}}\n| Filmed in 2018, released in 2019\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last=Clements |first=Sasha |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BgjcFGLghuc/?hl=en&taken-by=sashclements |publisher=[[Instagram]].com |title=Filming has begun! Sooooo excited \ud83d\ude0d.|date= |accessdate=March 20, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''Ovid and the Art of Love''\n| 2019\n| Ovid\n| {{sort|Hoffman|Esm\u00e9 von Hoffman}}\n| Filmed in 2015, released in 2019\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|}\n\n===TV movies===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical]]''\n| 2006\n| {{sort|Danforth|[[Chad Danforth]]}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/high_school_musical/ |title=High School Musical |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=May 23, 2006}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Jump In!]]''\n| 2007\n| {{sort|Daniels|Isadore \"Izzy\" Daniels}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/articles/keke-palmer-corbin-bleu-was-my-first-kiss-137946/ |title=Corbin Bleu had Keke Palmer feeling red after their kiss! |publisher=accesshollywood.com |date= |accessdate=September 24, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 2]]''\n| 2007\n| {{sort|Danforth|Chad Danforth}