s and Corbin Bleu to Star in Anything Goes |publisher=theatermania.com |date= |accessdate=August 16, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Kiss Me, Kate]]''\n|2019\n|Bill Calhoun/Lucentio\n|[[Studio 54]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Based on the 1953 [[Cole Porter]] and [[Bella and Samuel Spewack]], [[Kiss Me Kate (film)|film of the same name]].}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left; background:#ffc;\"| ''[[Catch Me If You Can (musical)|Catch Me If You Can]]'' {{dagger|alt=Theatre that have not yet been released}}\n| 2020\n|[[Frank Abagnale]]\n|Arena Stage\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Based on the 2002 [[Steven Spielberg]], [[Catch Me If You Can|film of the same name]].}}\n|-\n<!--do ''not'' put films that are 'in pre-production' or 'in development' per WP:CRYSTAL-->\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Voice role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical: Makin' the Cut!]]''\n| 2007\n| [[List of High School Musical characters#Chad Danforth|Chad Danforth]]\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical: Sing It!]]''\n| 2007\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames4\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 2: Work This Out!]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames1\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 3: Senior Year Dance]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames2\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 3: Senior Year (video game)|High School Musical 3: Senior Year DS]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film