as Brothers]])}} (2009)\n*''Disney Channel Summer At Sea'' {{small|(Co-headlining with [[Jonnie and Brookie]])}} (2009)\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:99%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Award\n! scope=\"col\"| Year of ceremony\n! scope=\"col\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\"| Nominee/work\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Los Angeles High School|LA High School for the Arts]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| 2005\n| \"Theatre Student of the Year\"\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.unigo.com/california_state_university-los_angeles/ | title=California State University-Los Angeles | work=Unigo.com | publisher= | date=July 11, 2005 | accessdate=July 11, 2005 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110702061959/http://www.unigo.com/california_state_university-los_angeles/ | archivedate=July 2, 2011 | df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Disney Channel New Years Bowl-A-Thon\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| 2006\n| \"Best Best Hair While Bowling\"\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"cp\">{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1135510/| title=New Year Sing-A-Long Bowl-A-Thon! In December 2006 | work=[[IMDb]].com | publisher= | date =December 31, 2006 | accessdate=December 31, 2006 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[NAACP Image Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"9\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 2007\n| \"Outstanding Performance in a Youth/Children's Program\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"| ''[[High School Musical]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|last=Katz |first=Nikki |url=http://www.juniorcelebs.com/corbin-bleu-helps-announce-naacp-image-awards-noms/ |title=Corbin Bleu was on hand for the 40th NAACP Image Awards nominees as they were announced today during 