ry/19/05/14/here-are-the-winners-of-the-helen-hayes-awards-for-local-theater/|archive-date=May 15, 2019|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Drama Desk Award]]\n| \"[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actor in a Musical|Outstanding Featured Actor in a Musical]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center\"| ''[[Kiss Me, Kate]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|last=Miller|first=Deb| url=https://dcmetrotheaterarts.com/2019/04/25/nominations-announced-for-the-2019-drama-desk-awards/ |publisher=dcmetrotheaterarts.com |title=Nominations Announced for the 2019 Drama Desk Awards|date= April 25, 2019|accessdate=April 25, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Chita Rivera Awards for Dance and Choreography]]\n| \"Outstanding Male Dancer in a Broadway Show\"\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|last=Hetrick|first=Adam| url=http://www.playbill.com/article/gabrielle-hamilton-corbin-bleu-amber-gray-more-nominated-for-2019-chita-rivera-awards |publisher=[[Playbill]].com |title=Gabrielle Hamilton, Corbin Bleu, Amber Gray, More Nominated for 2019 Chita Rivera Awards|date= April 26, 2019|accessdate=April 26, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Broadway.com Audience Awards|Audience Choice Awards]]\n| \"Favorite Featured Actor in a Musical\"\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref>{{cite web|last=Bowling|first=Suzanna| url=https://t2conline.com/broadway-com-audience-choice-awards-did-your-favorites-make-the-cut/ |publisher=[[Playbill]].com |title=Broadway.com Audience Choice Awards Did Your Favorites Make the Cut|date= |accessdate=May 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Jeffrey King]]\n* [[List of High School Musical characters|List of characters from High School Musical]]\n* [[Flight 29 Down#Characters|List of characters from Flight 29 Down]]\n* [[List of Italian-American actors]]\n* [[List of Italian-American entertainers]]\n* [[List of Jamaican Americans]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n==References