nbrew.com |date= April 13, 2011|accessdate=April 13, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''Twinkle Toes''\n| 2012\n| Drew (voice)\n| {{sort|Casalese|Mauro Casalese}}<br />{{sort|Woodgate|Dave Woodgate}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.awn.com/news/skechers-debuts-twinkle-toes-direct-dvd-movie-miptv |title=Next Post Skechers Debuts Twinkle Toes Direct-To-DVD Movie at MIPTV |publisher=awn.com |date= |accessdate=March 31, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Scary or Die]]''\n| 2012\n| Emmett\n| {{sort|Badway|Bob Badway}}<br />{{sort|Emanuel|Michael Emanuel}}<br />{{sort|Meglic|Igor Meglic}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last=Turek|first=Ryan|title=Do NOT Mess With This Clown from the Horror Anthology Scary or Die|url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/165181-do-not-mess-with-this-clown-from-the-horror-anthology-scary-or-die/|publisher=STYD|accessdate=April 2, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Nurse 3D]]''\n| 2013\n| Steve\n| {{sort|Aarniokoski|[[Doug Aarniokoski]]}}\n| Filmed in 2011, released in 2013\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{efn|group=upper-alpha|The film premiered on September to October 2011 in [[Toronto]], and released in [[Switzerland]] on September 28, 2013. and was eventually released [[Direct-to-DVD]] on February 7, 2014.}}\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Sugar (2013 film)|Sugar]]''\n| 2013\n| Sketch\n| {{sort|Rainwater|Rotimi Rainwater}}\n| Filmed in 2010, released in 2013\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{efn|group=upper-alpha|The film premiered on November 30, 2010 in [[Venice, Los Angeles]], and was released theatrically on September 6, 2013.}}\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[The Monkey's Paw (2013 film)|The Monkey's Paw]]''\n| 2013\n| Catfish\n| {{sort|Simmons|Brett Simmons}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/164075/corbin-bleu-to-star-in-new-tv-horror-movie-the-monkeys-paw/ |title=Corbin Bleu to Star in New TV Horror Movie The Monkey's Paw |publi