ing It!]]''\n| 2007\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames4\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 2: Work This Out!]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames1\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 3: Senior Year Dance]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames2\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[High School Musical 3: Senior Year (video game)|High School Musical 3: Senior Year DS]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames3\" />\n|-\n!scope=row| ''[[Disney Sing It! \u2013 High School Musical 3: Senior Year]]''\n| 2008\n| Chad Danforth\n| Based on the film\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"HSMVideogames5\" />\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Performer(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Don't Be Shy\"\n| style=\"text-align:center| 2008\n| Small Change<br />Chani<br />[[Lil' JJ]]\n| ''Concrete & Clay''\n| style=\"text-align:center\"|<ref name=\"ReferenceM\" />\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n{{Main|Corbin Bleu discography|List of songs recorded by Corbin Bleu}}\n\n===Studio albums===\n*''[[Another Side (Corbin Bleu album)|Another Side]]'' (2007)\n*''[[Speed of Light (album)|Speed of Light]]'' (2009)\n\n===Soundtrack albums===\n*''[[High School Musical (soundtrack)|High School Musical]]'' (2006)\n*''[[Jump In!#Soundtrack|Jump In!]]'' (2007)\n*''[[High School Musical 2 (soundtrack)|High School Musical 2]]'' (2007)\n*''[[High School Musical 3: Senior Year (soundtrack)|High School Musical 3: Senior Year]]'' (2008)\n*''[[Holiday Inn (musical)#Song list|Holiday Inn, The New Irving Berlin Musical]]'' (2017)\n*''[[Kiss Me, Kate#S